PurgeActionResultMainCard is a CardView
    show labels
    main column
        BusinessView
        BusinessAction
        RunTimeStamp
            italics
        EndTimeStamp
            italics
    right column
        text of "Restored"
            display as tag
                color of blue
            visible when (IsFullyRestored)
        text of untranslatable:"<YellowAlertMessage>"
            display as tag
                color of yellow
            visible when (RaiseYellowAlert)
